| **1** (foundation) | P2T1, P2T2 | API types + client functions, Zustand store + TanStack hooks |
| **2** (components) | P2T3, P2T4, P2T5, P2T6, P2T7 | KPI Grid, Morning Brief, Alerts Feed, Timeline + Status + QuickActions, Notification Bell |
| **3** (assembly) | P2T8 | Dashboard page wiring, barrel exports, layout integration |

**Key design decisions:**
- TanStack Query for all data fetching (auto-refresh, caching, loading states)
- Zustand store for user preferences (collapsed sections, dismissed alerts) — persisted to localStorage
- RBAC via `useRole()` in page.tsx — role determines which variant renders (no per-component gates needed)
- Alert dismiss stored client-side (localStorage) — backend gap workaround
- Notification bell polls `/alerts` every 60s; dashboard widgets refresh every 5 min
- Reuses existing MarkdownRenderer from P1 for brief rendering
- 14 new files, 2 modified files, zero file overlap between parallel tasks
